        </subfigure>
        
      <caption>A single complex-valued signal must be displayed in two plots; here the real and imaginary parts are plotted.</caption></figure><figure xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" id="fig6" orient="vertical"><subfigure id="fig6s1">
